sentences: Oluseun Anikulapo Kuti (born 11 January 1983), who is called by the name Seun Kuti, is a Nigerian musician, singer and the youngest son of the famous Afrobeat pioneer, Fela Kuti.
The youngest son of Fela Kuti, Kuti was born in 1983.
Fela Kuti died in 1997 and Seun Kuti took to the role of leading Egypt 80.
